00:36:23,881 --> 00:36:26,684
(dramatic music)

601
00:36:31,155 --> 00:36:33,891
(ice crinkling)

602
00:36:58,716 --> 00:37:00,451
- What the hell 
are you doing here?

603
00:37:00,518 --> 00:37:01,986
Get off the ice.

604
00:37:03,221 --> 00:37:08,426
(dramatic music) 
(blade smashing)

605
