- (sighing) Oh you had 
nothing to do with this.

606
00:37:28,879 --> 00:37:31,582
- Why would I harm a 
person I barely knew?

607
00:37:31,649 --> 00:37:33,351
- (sighing) When it comes 
to shopping for murder,

608
00:37:33,417 --> 00:37:35,086
you're something of 
an impulse buyer.

609
00:37:35,152 --> 00:37:37,488
- I hope this doesn't impede 
Jessica Ann's progress

610
00:37:37,555 --> 00:37:38,689
with her skating.

611
00:37:38,756 --> 00:37:41,826
