- I was there in the 
afternoon, just watching.

614
00:37:46,831 --> 00:37:49,834
- I have witness 
statements Mrs. Sterling.

615
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:52,937
- I merely told Jessica 
Ann that we shouldn't talk,

616
00:37:53,004 --> 00:37:55,573
that the court didn't 
want us to have contact.

617
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:57,241
- But you did have contact!

618
00:37:57,308 --> 00:38:00,578
- There was an 
inch of plexiglass 
separating us Sergeant.

