00:38:00,645 --> 00:38:02,513
- It's gonna have to be 
reported to the court.

620
00:38:02,580 --> 00:38:06,350
- Don't you report all 
murders to the court?

621
00:38:06,417 --> 00:38:09,353
- I am talking about 
seeing your daughter.

622
00:38:09,420 --> 00:38:11,889
- Sergeant, a man is dead.

623
00:38:11,956 --> 00:38:13,324
And you're concerned 
about keeping

624
00:38:13,391 --> 00:38:14,925
a mother from her daughter.

625
00:38:14,992 --> 00:38:16,494
Where are your values?

626
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:18,429
- And where were you at 
the time of the murder?

627
00:38:18,496 --> 00:38:20,564
Let's cut the 
chitchat here lady.

628
00:38:20,631 --> 00:38:21,699
- Haven't you heard?

629
00:38:21,766 --> 00:38:24,035
I have an implant 
that makes me behave.

630
00:38:24,101 --> 00:38:25,369
- You got an implant?

631
00:38:25,436 --> 00:38:26,671
I tell you what I think.

632
00:38:26,737 --> 00:38:28,639
I think you implanted 
that hockey skate

