00:39:43,114 --> 00:39:44,215
but I put him off.

651
00:39:44,281 --> 00:39:45,182
- What?

652
00:39:45,249 --> 00:39:46,817
Why, I'm not a baby.

653
00:39:46,884 --> 00:39:49,453
- I know, but you've 
been through so much.

654
00:39:49,520 --> 00:39:50,654
- Is mommy all right?

655
00:39:50,721 --> 00:39:53,491
- Oh, she's all right, 
all right physically.

