(school belling ringing)

730
00:43:03,447 --> 00:43:08,652
(chattering) 
(doors banging)

731
00:43:17,695 --> 00:43:18,729
- Are you okay?

732
00:43:18,796 --> 00:43:19,897
- Sure.

733
00:43:19,964 --> 00:43:21,599
- Are you ready for 
the history test?

734
00:43:21,665 --> 00:43:22,766
- I guess.

735
00:43:22,833 --> 00:43:25,202
- You shouldn't listen 
to what kids say.

736
00:43:25,269 --> 00:43:26,537
- Who says I listen?

737
00:43:26,604 --> 00:43:28,973
- Nobody, I just thought at 
lunch you might have heard

