- Just don't pay any 
attention to them, that's all.

740
00:43:32,509 --> 00:43:34,912
- (sighing) Whatever. 
- Jessica Ann, I, I'm sorry

741
00:43:34,979 --> 00:43:37,648
I didn't meant to 
scare you, honey.

