00:43:37,715 --> 00:43:38,949
- You're not 
supposed to be here.

743
00:43:39,016 --> 00:43:41,385
- I had to see you. 
- I'm not supposed to see you.

744
00:43:41,452 --> 00:43:42,553
You're gonna go back to jail.

745
00:43:42,620 --> 00:43:44,088
- That's why we have to talk.

746
00:43:44,154 --> 00:43:47,758
You know, your skating 
instructor, that 
terrible accident.

747
00:43:47,825 --> 00:43:49,159
- It wasn't an accident.

748
00:43:49,226 --> 00:43:52,229
You don't accidentally get 
stabbed a hundred times.

749
00:43:52,296 --> 00:43:53,230
- I didn't do.

750
00:43:53,297 --> 00:43:55,699
I didn't do it, you 
have to believe me.

751
00:43:55,766 --> 00:43:56,834
- I do.

752
00:43:58,168 --> 00:43:59,403
- You do?

753
00:43:59,470 --> 00:44:00,804
Do you really?

