755
00:44:06,410 --> 00:44:07,411
- Oh my god.

756
00:44:08,545 --> 00:44:09,546
You hate me, don't you?

757
00:44:09,613 --> 00:44:11,248
- No, I don't hate you.

758
00:44:11,315 --> 00:44:14,518
- Jessica Ann, who's 
your next class?

759
00:44:14,585 --> 00:44:16,453
- Er, first floor west wing.

